'''Master chief petty officer''' was a rank/rate in several services.

It was known to exist in the [[Royal Alderaan Civil Fleet/Legends|Royal Alderaan Civil Fleet]], where it was held by [[Corla Metonae/Legends|Corla Metonae]] when she was transferred to the [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']], and in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]], where it was held by [[Tenn Graneet]].

